			</div>
			<div class="right-nav">
				<h2>Blog</h2>
				<p>Discover a treasure trove of captivating golf blogs that delve into the latest trends,
					 tips, and stories from the world of golf.</p>
				
			</div>
			<div class="deco">
				<img src="/golf-list/images/deco.webp" alt="" srcset="">
